Today's Riddle is -


Which is correct to say, 'The yolk of the egg are white' or,'The yolk
of the egg is white'?





As always, you will find the answer below today's sponsor.




Please take a moment and visit today's sponsor-

-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-

-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-:-



The answer to today's Riddle is -

Neither!  The yolk of the egg is yellow.


